{"tid":2510543,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大英帝國海軍重返亞洲","createTime":"2021-04-30T08:38:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T08:41:17.000Z","uid":101555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8f44aca514d54601e51c39da6e5148be11b43306","tid":2510543,"uid":101555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T08:38:04.000Z","msg":"英國國防部周一說，英國近年來最大的海軍艦隊將於5月啟航，航行長達一個月，穿越太平洋。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;當我們的行動打擊群（CSG）下個月啟航時，它將為全球英國人懸掛旗幟-展示我們的影響力，表達我們的力量，與我們的朋友互動，並重申我們致力於應對當今和明天的安全挑戰 &rdquo;，英國國防部長本&middot;華萊士（Ben Wallace）週一表示。<br />\n<br />\n華萊士說：&ldquo;英國不是後退，而是揚帆起航，在塑造21世紀國際體系中發揮積極作用。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n打擊群將由航母伊麗莎白女王號領導，標誌著其首次部署。 這艘船是英國的兩艘航母之一，是英國有史以來最大的軍艦。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWpQxxpPrqb6NRCgSc4i5WLCBzy95rZtYeeYzbFRpVCMq?filename=gcN5Yts.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgcN5Yts.jpg&h=45690d39&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38fd4f844bbb834f66df59d4fd025d93cb254613","tid":2510543,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T08:39:56.000Z","msg":"依家國力真係夠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aaa881c46da8b94e871474fb7abba02b412a9ea","tid":2510543,"uid":101555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38fd4f844bbb834f66df59d4fd025d93cb254613","tid":2510543,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T08:39:56.000Z","msg":"依家國力真係夠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T08:41:17.000Z","msg":"唔夠<br />\n但五眼加埋easy win"}]}